item.title: Kontakt
item.description:
<form class="custom-font-white font-Thasadith" accept-charset="UTF-8" action="https://formspree.io/f/xvgojggw" method="POST" role="form">
<label class="custom-font-white font-Thasadith f6 b db mb1 mt3 sans-serif white" for="name">Dein Name</label> <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="w-100 f5 pv3 ph3 bg-light-gray bn" required placeholder=" " aria-labelledby="name"/>
<label class="custom-font-white font-Thasadith f6 b db mb1 mt3 sans-serif white" for="email">Email Adresse</label> <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="w-100 f5 pv3 ph3 bg-light-gray bn" required placeholder=" " aria-labelledby="email"/>
<label class="custom-font-white font-Thasadith f6 b db mb1 mt3 sans-serif white" for="message">Nachricht</label> <textarea id="message" name="message" class="w-100 f5 pv3 ph3 bg-light-gray bn h4" aria-labelledby="message"></textarea>
<input class="db w-100 mv2 custom-font-white-90 pa3 bn hover-shadow bg-animate custom-bg-light-red" type="submit" value="Senden" />
</form>
